<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 21:15:25 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>报告称，俄罗斯、伊朗、中国预计将利用人工智能试图影响美国大选</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/russia-iran-china-expected-use-ai-try-influence-us-election-report-says-2024-10-02/</link><description>根据周三发布的美国年度威胁评估，美国认为俄罗斯、伊朗和中国试图影响 11 月 5 日选举的威胁越来越大，包括利用人工智能传播虚假或分裂性信息。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 18:05:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/russia-iran-china-expected-use-ai-try-influence-us-election-report-says-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>解说：伊朗主要核设施长期处于以色列的视线之中</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/irans-main-nuclear-facilities-long-israels-sights-2024-10-02/</link><description>周二伊朗对以色列发动导弹袭击后，有人猜测以色列可能会像其长期以来威胁的那样袭击伊朗的核设施。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 17:46:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/irans-main-nuclear-facilities-long-israels-sights-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>中央情报局将在线招募线人扩大到中国、伊朗和朝鲜</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/cia-expands-online-recruitment-informants-china-iran-north-korea-2024-10-02/</link><description>美国中央情报局周三启动了一项新的行动，在中国、伊朗和朝鲜招募线人，这在其所称的招募俄罗斯人的成功努力的基础上又进一步加强了。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 16:12:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/cia-expands-online-recruitment-informants-china-iran-north-korea-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>越南抗议中国军队在争议海域袭击渔民</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-protests-chinese-forces-attack-fishermen-contested-waters-2024-10-02/</link><description>越南周三向中国提出抗议，称三天前一艘越南渔船在有争议的南中国海海域遭到袭击，造成数名渔民受伤。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 15:19:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-protests-chinese-forces-attack-fishermen-contested-waters-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>梅赛德斯CEO：打破中国“信心危机”最重要</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/mercedes-ceo-breaking-chinas-confidence-crisis-is-most-important-thing-2024-10-02/</link><description>梅赛德斯-奔驰首席执行官奥拉·康林松表示，结束中国消费者信心危机是梅赛德斯-奔驰中短期内最重要的事情，并将汽车市场描述为一场“达尔文之战”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 13:19:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/mercedes-ceo-breaking-chinas-confidence-crisis-is-most-important-thing-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>小鹏汽车：我们来欧洲是为了带来技术</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xpeng-we-are-coming-europe-bring-technology-2024-10-02/</link><description>中国电动汽车制造商小鹏汽车董事会副主席兼联席总裁布莱恩·顾表示，该汽车制造商不打算在欧洲销售其汽车以提供廉价替代品，而是为了带来自己的技术。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 13:12:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xpeng-we-are-coming-europe-bring-technology-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>美国将拨款高达 1 亿美元，以促进人工智能在半导体材料中的应用</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/us-award-up-100-million-boost-use-ai-semiconductor-materials-2024-10-02/</link><description>美国商务部周三表示，计划拨款 1 亿美元，以促进人工智能在开发新型可持续半导体材料中的应用。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 13:06:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/us-award-up-100-million-boost-use-ai-semiconductor-materials-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>阿尔卡拉斯反击击败卫冕冠军辛纳夺得中国公开赛冠军</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/alcaraz-fights-back-down-defending-champion-sinner-win-china-open-2024-10-02/</link><description>卡洛斯·阿尔卡拉斯在周三的中国公开赛决赛中，在先失一盘的情况下奋起直追，在决定性的抢七中顽强拼搏，以 6-7(6) 6-4 7-6(3) 击败卫冕冠军詹尼克·辛纳，夺得个人第四个网球冠军。季节。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 13:03:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/alcaraz-fights-back-down-defending-champion-sinner-win-china-open-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>马里诺队击败蔚山队，使亚冠联赛重回正轨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/marinos-put-asian-champions-league-campaign-back-track-with-ulsan-thrashing-2024-10-02/</link><description>横滨水手队周三从首日耻辱中恢复过来，在日本以 4-0 击败韩国蔚山 HD，让他们的亚洲冠军联赛精英赛重回正轨。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 12:49:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/marinos-put-asian-champions-league-campaign-back-track-with-ulsan-thrashing-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>通用汽车寻求在投资者日缓解股东的紧张情绪</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/gm-seeks-ease-shareholders-nerves-investor-day-2024-10-02/</link><description>投资者对汽车制造商的利润感到担忧，因为他们在电动汽车方面面临重大损失，燃气发动机汽车的销售陷入停滞，而且来自中国的压力不断加大。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 12:47:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/gm-seeks-ease-shareholders-nerves-investor-day-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>大众汽车呼吁德国投票反对欧盟对中国汽车征收关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-calls-germany-vote-against-eu-tariffs-chinese-cars-2024-10-02/</link><description>大众汽车周三敦促德国投票反对欧盟对中国电动汽车征收关税，称关税并不能提高汽车行业的竞争力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 12:30:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-calls-germany-vote-against-eu-tariffs-chinese-cars-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，欧盟有足够的支持对中国电动汽车征收关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/france-greece-italy-poland-set-back-chinese-ev-tariffs-sources-say-2024-10-02/</link><description>消息人士称，法国、希腊、意大利和波兰将于周五投票支持对中国制造的电动汽车（EV）进口征收高达 45% 的关税，这足以推动欧盟最引人注目的贸易措施，但可能面临报复风险来自北京。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 12:18:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/france-greece-italy-poland-set-back-chinese-ev-tariffs-sources-say-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>德国肖尔茨呼吁与中国就电动汽车进行更多谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/germanys-scholz-talks-with-china-electric-vehicles-must-continue-2024-10-02/</link><description>德国总理奥拉夫·肖尔茨周三表示，排除外国竞争并缩小贸易伙伴范围的做法是错误的，并表示必须继续与中国就电动汽车进行谈判。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 11:30:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/germanys-scholz-talks-with-china-electric-vehicles-must-continue-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟要求 YouTube、Snapchat、TikTok 提供有关内容算法的信息</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/eu-requests-information-youtube-snapchat-tiktok-about-recommendations-2024-10-02/</link><description>周三，欧盟委员会要求 YouTube、Snapchat 和 TikTok 提供信息，了解其算法向用户推荐内容所使用的参数，以及它们在放大一些系统性风险（包括与选举过程、心理健康和未成年人保护相关的风险）方面所扮演的角色。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 10:14:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/eu-requests-information-youtube-snapchat-tiktok-about-recommendations-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：中东紧张局势、港口罢工导致第四季度开局紧张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-10-02/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 10:02:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-10-02/</guid></item></channel></rss>